@startuml SelfHostedAuthFlow
title TIMELAPSE - Autenticação Self-Hosted (SRS 4.2)
actor User
participant Browser
participant SelfHostedServer
participant AuthService
participant EmailService

User -> Browser: Acessa timelapse.internal.company.com
Browser -> SelfHostedServer: GET /login
SelfHostedServer -> Browser: Página de Login

User -> Browser: Informa Email
Browser -> SelfHostedServer: POST /auth/magic-link {email}
SelfHostedServer -> AuthService: Solicita Magic Link
AuthService -> EmailService: Envia Token (domínio interno)
EmailService -> User: Recebe Email

User -> Browser: Clica no Link
Browser -> SelfHostedServer: GET /auth/verify?token=...
SelfHostedServer -> AuthService: Valida Token
AuthService -> SelfHostedServer: JWT + User
SelfHostedServer -> Browser: Redireciona para App
Browser -> User: Acesso Liberado (organização interna)
@enduml
